C Korea] . A recent survey stated that about one million dogs are sold every year for food in [LOC South Korea] and 92 percent of men aged 20 and above and 68 percent of adult women have tasted dog meat . 2002-01-15 [LOC Pakistan] ( PK ) ; [LOC India] ( [LOC IN] ) International ; Government ; terrorism ; war and conflict ; dissent ; leader Religious extremism continues in [LOC Pakistan] despite the banning of militant groups . Religious extremism continues in [LOC Pakistan] despite the banning of militant groups by the [MISC Pakistani] Government . Newspapers and magazines extolling the virtues of [MISC Islamic] holy war in [LOC Kashmir] continue to fill the newstands in [LOC Pakistan] despite the [MISC Pakistani] military Government 's attempt at a large scale containment of religious extremism . Around 1400 alleged religious extremists have been arrested since 020112 under severe actions against [MISC Islamic] militants and sectarian radicals announced by President [PER Pervez Musharraf] during the weekend . The severe actions against militants and radicals came as [PER Pervez Musharraf] banned 5 [MISC Islamic] groups . The banned 5 [MISC Islamic] groups included the 2 hardline militant groups fighting [MISC Indian] rule in [LOC Kashmir] which the [MISC Indian] government accuses of staging the violent 011213 attack on the [MISC Indian] parliament . [MISC Pakistani] authorities have stated that no statements or literature from the 5 banned [MISC Islamic] groups would be tolerated after [PER Pervez Musharraf] 's speech banning the 5 [MISC Islamic] groups . [PER Pervez Musharraf] 's speech banning the 5 [MISC Islamic] groups was applauded by the [LOC United States] . [PER Iftikhar Ahmed] stated that under the notification that was issued late at night on 020114 all publications , newspapers , weekly magazines , monthlies , etc of the 5 banned [MISC Islamic] groups are banned and confiscated . [PER Iftikhar Ahmed] is a [MISC Pakistani] interior ministry official . [P