rcentages apply to the [MISC Internet] as a whole . [PER Edelman] told [ORG AFP] that it is highly likely that approximately one-tenth of the [MISC Internet] is filtered by or recently has been filtered by [LOC China] . [PER Edelman] stated that there are many different ways to measure this effect and therefore hesitated to specify any single proportion . The latest study was broader than prior surveys and gives perspective to disparate reports about websites that are filtered or blocked by [LOC China] . In the report it is concluded that -- [LOC China] blocks a range of web content beyond that which is sexually explicit . 1000s of sites providing information about news , health , education , and entertainment were blocked . Approximately 3284 sites from [LOC Taiwan] were blocked . The blocked sites also included those of [LOC U.S.] news organizations including [ORG ABC News] and [ORG CBS News] , the [ORG Alta Vista] search engine , and a number of [LOC U.S.] universities . The researchers found that 100 percent of the top 10 sites with keywords [LOC Tibet] , [LOC Taiwan] [LOC China] , or equality were blocked . A large number of other sites with keywords such as freedom , democracy and [MISC HIV] were also blocked . The [ORG BBC] news site was consistently unavailable . Sites for [ORG CNN] , Time magazine , [MISC U.S.-based] public broadcasting system , the [ORG Miami Herald] , and the [ORG Philadelphia Inquirer] were also often blocked . The report found that 42 of google 's top 100 results for news were blocked . Religious sites blocked in [LOC China] included the [MISC Asian] [ORG American Baptist Church] , The atheist network , the [ORG Catholic Civil Rights League] , [PER Feng Shui] , the [ORG Jewish Federation] of [LOC Winnipeg] , and the [MISC Denver Zen] center . [LOC China] has an estimated 45 million [MISC Internet] users . [LOC China] has been widely criticized in the West for blocking websites and for imprisoning people for viewing banned sites or using the [MISC Internet] for anti-government activities . The [MISC Chinese] government is believed to routinely block a large number of foreign-based sites primarily those featuring dissident views or banned groups such as the Falungong spiritual organization but also certain foreign news sites and pages showing pornography . A recent report by the [MISC U.S.-based] [ORG Rand Corporation] think tank found that the [MISC Chinese] government now uses more technology to filter out objectionable content rather than relying solely on surveillance of users and seizure of equipment as it did in the past . The rand report released earlier in 2002 found that [MISC Chinese] authorities now appear to have more effective technology for filtering out undesirable content . 2002-12-10 [LOC Europe] ; [LOC Iraq] ( IQ ) proliferation ; international ; science A laboratory chief from the [ORG International Atomic Energy Agency] ( [ORG IAEA] ) said on December 10 , 2002 that the [ORG UN] 's nuclear agency could detect even infinitesimal amounts of radiation from weapons programs if they exist in samples from [LOC Iraq] . A laboratory chief from the [ORG International Atomic Energy Agency] ( [ORG IAEA] ) said on December 10 , 2002 that the [ORG UN] 's nuclear agency could detect infinitesimal amounts of radiation from weapons programs if they exist in samples from [LOC Iraq] . [PER David Donohue] spoke at the [ORG IAEA] laboratory in [LOC Seibersdorf] on the southwest outskirts of [LOC Vienna] . [PER Donohue] said the equipment can detect particles down to the picogram ( a millionth of a millionth of a gram ) . The first samples from [LOC Iraq] are due to arrive to the laboratory this week . [ORG IAEA] and other [ORG UN] inspectors have been taking soil , water and air samples since November 27 , 2001 at [MISC Iraqi] sites suspected of being used for programs to make weapons of mass destruction . [PER Donohue] said samples will be sent for corroboration to labs in [LOC France] , the [LOC U