00 but it did not inflict widespread damage . [PER Sadagopan] addressed delegates at a conference on information security . [PER Sadagopan] stated that these things happen with all technology if history is reviewed and that imaginative people can cause extraordinary problems even with primitive technology . [PER Sadagopan] said the [ORG G8 nations] have lost 43 billion dollars due to cyber crime . The [ORG G8 nations] are comprised of [LOC France] , [LOC Britain] , [LOC Canada] , [LOC Germany] , [LOC Italy] , [LOC Japan] , [LOC Russia] and the [LOC United States] . [PER Sadagopan] said most people have an alarmist view of such attacks . The attacks range from viruses , flame-mail ( abusive e-mail ) , stone throwing ( disfiguring a home page ) to cyber squatters and scripts for breaking into [MISC Internet] sites . [PER Sadagopan] stated that many sensitive installations such as nuclear and power plants , and missiles have an [MISC Internet] protocol address and that once someone hacks into the sites one can trip the power lines or lead planes and missiles to their choice destinations . [PER Sadagopan] added that this type of hacking is possible , but there is no need to panic . [PER Sadagopan] said it needs to be recognized and while we should be sensitive about such threats it should not be sensationalized rather a pragmatic approach should be taken . The [ORG U.S. State Department] said in May 2002 that a computer [PER Hacker] had infiltrated its e-mail system . The [PER Hacker] sent a potentially damaging virus to more than 20000 people who receive travel warnings electronically . A 50-line code of the love bug virus affects more than 2.8 million files monthly . Hackers have sent love letter e-mail to all chosen Heads of States from adolfahitler.com . [ORG Pentagon] sites had denial of service for more than three hours . [LOC India] 's premier nuclear research center [ORG Bhabha Atomic] resarch center sites were disfigured . [PER Sadagopan] stated that a section 